Project Manager Responsibilities towards the team members
	- At first, he must has a good understanding of the project and its tasks, so he can assign the right task to the right team member.
	- Which leads to his responsibility to know the qualifications of each member of the team.
	- He must always keep in touch with them as a team and with each one indiviualy to solve any problem comes up
	- He must know how to get the best out of each one by motivating them.
	- Also sometimes he should be strict to ensure the best output at the right time.
	- Make sure that all the team members help each other in their tasks and review each other.
	- The PM also has to help them as a team member (to be one of them more than a boss).
